00:06:46.360 --> 00:06:48.440
Seperti bibi, seperti keponakan!

00:06:48.520 --> 00:06:50.800
Keponakanmu Ravi Randhawa

00:06:51.000 --> 00:06:54.000
menikahi putriku secara
paksa di luar keinginannya!

00:06:56.880 --> 00:06:58.640
Sebentar.

